_Auberginefleur at Japan Now & Then_ has compiled [a handy list of Tokyo's
firework
events](http://blog.livedoor.jp/auberginefleur/archives/51690828.html) for
2009. [suzurzan.ranran](http://www.flickr.com/photos/suzuran-
ranran/sets/72157621706729497/), [cadm2](http://www.flickr.com/photos/cadm2/),
[chris.jan](http://www.flickr.com/photos/chrisjan99/sets/72157621834452854/)
have uploaded their photos of yesterday's Sumidagawa Fireworks Festival, one
of Tokyo's biggest summer events.

